Nowadays we are living in such a age, where one knows that what will happen in next moment? In such scenario what we can do is to be stay aware each moment. CRIME TAK is here to help and assist you in this regard, by making you aware of all crime related incidents/stories, so that you can be safe.

snippet.title: सत्यपाल मलिक से बातचीत | Interview with Satyapal Malik
snippet.description:
करण थापर से सत्यपाल मलिक की बातचीत: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b8wmHUhLvOI 

करण थापर के इंटर्व्यू से उठे सवालों पर हमारी विस्तृत रिपोर्ट: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2MZKZhR5TYQ

यह बताना  ज़रूरी है कि द वायर के लिए करण थापर ने सत्यपाल मलिक का शानदार इंटरव्यू किया है। उनके ही इंटरव्यू के बाद संदर्भ बना तभी मैंने इंटरव्यू किया। आप करण थापर का भी इंटरव्यू पूरा देखें। वे अपने सवालों को लेकर बहुत मेहनत करते हैं। तो मेरे भी इंटरव्यू का श्रेय करण थापर को जाता है। सत्यपाल मलिक ने जो कहा उस पर सरकार चुप है। उसकी चुप्पी से ज़्यादा दुख की बात यह है कि कांग्रेस पार्टी की प्रेस कांफ्रेंस को गोदी मीडिया ने नहीं दिखाया। अख़बारों में भी टेलिग्राफ को छोड़ कर किसी ने नहीं छापा। उम्मीद है मेरा इंटरव्यू आपके किसी काम का होगा। 
शुक्रिया, 
रवीश कुमार

It is pertinent to note here that Karan Thapar has done a brilliant interview of Satyapal Malik for The Wire. His interview gave rise to a set of questions that led me to further speak with Mr Malik. I urge you to please watch that interview in its entirety. Mr Thapar undertakes a lot of effort for his questions, and so the credit for my interview ultimately lies with him. The government has maintained a steady silence on Satyapal Malik's interview. Perhaps it is more unfortunate that Godi Media did not give any coverage to the Congress Party's press conference. No newspaper - with the exception of The Telegraph - gave any coverage to this interview. I hope my interview will be of some merit to you. 
Thank you, 
Ravish Kumar 

#ravishkumar #satyapalmalik #interview #modi #rajnathsingh #bjp #congress #kashmir #crpf #karanthapar  #jammukashmir #governor #thewire #news #latestnews

snippet.title: 1 Year For KGF Chapter 2 | Yash | Prashanth Neel | Vijay Kiragandur | Sanjay Dutt | Hombale Films
snippet.description:
One year ago today, #KGFChapter2 took us on an unforgettable journey filled with breathtaking action, intense emotions and larger-than-life characters. The film's release was nothing short of a festival, with fans celebrating in theaters around the world. We're humbled by the incredible response to the film and grateful to everyone who made it such a success. Here's to the power of storytelling and the magic of cinema!

#1ROCKYingYearOfKGF2

Written and Directed by Prashanth Neel
Produced by Vijay Kiragandur under the Banner "Hombale Films".
Starring: Rocking Star Yash, Sanjay Dutt, Srinidhi Shetty, Raveena Tandon, Prakash Raj, Malvika Avinash, Achyuth Kumar, Ayyappa P. Sharma, Rao Ramesh, Eshwari Rao, Archana Jois, T. S. snippet.title: Allu Arha as Prince Bharata - Telugu Promo | Shaakuntalam | Samantha | Gunasekhar| Dil Raju
snippet.description:
Shaakuntalam Movie also in 3D, Written & Directed by Gunasekhar, Presented by Dil Raju under Sri Venkateswara Creations in collaboration with Gunaa Teamworks, Produced by Neelima Guna.

The massively mounted film Shaakuntalam based on internationally acclaimed Kalidasa’s Sanskrit play ‘Abhijnana Shakuntalam’ is all set to release in Hindi, Telugu, Tamil, Malayalam & Kannada.  The story of Shaakuntalam revolves around the epic love story of Shakuntala and King Dushyant from Mahabharata, portrayed by Samantha and Dev Mohan.

The film is helmed by supremely proficient, Director Gunasekhar and marks a whimsical tale of love set in the Kashyapa Kanumalu (Kashmir), the grandeur and splendour of Dushyant’s Puru Dynasty making the film extremely exceptional.

Cast and Crew Details: 

Shaakuntalam starring Samantha, Dev Mohan, Allu Arha, Sachin Khedekar, Kabir Bedi, Dr.M Mohan Babu, Prakash Raj, Madhubala, Gautami, Aditi Balan, Ananya Nagalla, Jisshu Sengupta and others

A Film By Gunasekhar
Producer: Neelima Guna
Presentor: Dil Raju
Music: ManiSharma
Editor: Prawin Pudi
Cinematography: Shekar V Joseph
Art: Ashok
VFX Supervisor: Alagarsamy Mayan
Lyrics: Chaitanya Prasad & Shreemani

snippet.description:

Dhyan Sreenivasan is an Indian actor, and film director who works in Malayalam films.Dhyan Sreenivasan was born on December 20, 1988 in Thalassery, Kerala, India. Dhyan Sreenivasan made his acting debut with Thira, directed by Dhyan Sreenivasan elder brother Vineeth Sreenivasan. Dhyan is the younger son of noted actor and screenwriter Sreenivasan. Dhyan Sreenivasan brother Vineeth Sreenivasan is a singer, actor and director who also works in Malayalam cinema. Dhyan married his longtime girlfriend Arpita Sebastian on 7 April 2017. He made his film debut with the Malayalam film Thira which has Shobana in main lead role. In the film, Dhyan Sreenivasan did a supporting role along with two-time National Award winning actress Shobana. His performance in the film was generally well-received by critics and the audience.

snippet.title: Death Threats, Sidhu Moose Wala & SRK's Support - @YoYoHoneySingh  | Figuring Out | EP 85
snippet.description:
Order my first book 'Build, Don't Talk' here: https://amzn.eu/d/eCfijRu

--------------
In today’s episode of Figuring Out, Raj talks with Honey Singh, AKA Hirdesh Singh an Indian music producer, rapper, singer, songwriter and an actor and has been widely loved in the Hindi as well as Punjabi Film Industry. Hailing from Delhi,  Singh prefers to sing in Hindi and his native language Punjabii rather than English.

Singh shares how his life is a manifestation of what he wanted it to be like and how he’s been blessed to have received mentorship & support from the who’s who of the industry like Shah Rukh Khan, Salman Khan, Akshay Kumar, & Amitabh Bachchan. 

Honey Singh has finally broken his silence for the first time ever on ‘Mafia Mundeer’, a group of boys he made music with back in Punjab and the reasons behind breaking it off. 


Having gone through a tough journey of Bipolar Disorder, Singh speaks openly about dealing with mental illness, his symptoms, treatment and the struggle he went through during this time. 

Make sure you watch this video till the end!


-------------------------

https://open.spotify.com/show/736rhmW7vilNgkFFo8aDz4

-------------

snippet.title: மதுரை பரோட்டா சால்னா | Madurai Famous Parotta Salna Recipe | CDK 1179 | Chef Deena's Kitchen
snippet.description:
Parotta Salna
INGREDIENTS  

Groundnut Oil – 400 ml
Shallots – ½ Kg
Green Chilli – 20 Nos
Whole Garam Mixed (Bay Leaf, Cinnamon Sticks, Cloves, Kalpasi, Cardamom – 15gm)
Ginger Paste – 1 Ladle
Garlic Paste – 3 Ladle
Country Tomato – 500 G
Mint – 2 Hand Full
Coriander – 1 Hand Full
Mutton With Bones – 1 Kg
Mutton Fat – 200 G
Curry Leaves  - As Required 
Turmeric Powder  - 3 Tsp
Cumin Powder – 3 Ladle
Fennel Powder – 2 Tsp
Pepper Powder – 5 Tsp
 Coriander Powder – 1 Ladle
Red Chilli Powder – ½ Ladle
Chilli Powder – 1 Ladle
Salt – As Required
Coconut – 8 Nos
Peanut – 50 G
Roasted Channa – 50 G
Coconut Milk – 1 Ladle
Nutmeg Powder – ½ piece

Apart from being a TV cookery host, my experience lies mainly with being employed in some of the major star hotels across the country especially the Marriott group.

 अतीक अहमद और अशरफ की प्रशासन की मौजूदगी में हत्या को लेकर निकिता चतुर्वेदी ने गंभीर सवाल उठाए साथ ही उन्होंने उन लोगों पर भी निशाना साधा जो जय श्री राम का नारा लगाकर इस तरह की वारदात को अंजाम देते हैं. इंटरव्यू को लेकर आपका जो कुछ भी कहना है कमेंट बॉक्स में आकर अपनी राय जरूर दें.
Desclaimer - वीडियो में बोले गए वक्ता के निजी विचार हैं चैनल ए आर न्यूज़ इंडिया इसकी पुष्टि नहीं करता हमारा मकसद किसी भी धर्म जाति समुदाय वर्ग को ठेस पहुंचाना नहीं है।

*About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

#CheapvsExpensive #Foodiwe #Foodiwechallange

If you're a foodie, you won't want to miss this Cheap vs Expensive Food Challenge!  In this food challenge, we'll be testing cheap and expensive food #products and see which one is better in the eyes of the food critic!

This food challenge is perfect for food #lovers of all levels of price sensitivity. If you're looking for a challenging food challenge that will have you comparing prices and tastes, then this is the video for you! 

Here we'll compare the taste, texture, and overall quality of expensive food vs cheap food. snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3746 - 15 Apr 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3746: Car Coupon
--------------------------------------------------------
Rustom Ji and his assistant visit the Gada shop to collect the coupons for the lucky draw. At first, Rustom Ji facilitates Jetha with a "certificate of appreciation". Jetha offers some tasty faloodas to Rustom Ji. Jetha deliberately tries to avoid discussions about the coupons, so he brings up irrelevant topics. Anyway, when Rustom Ji asks for the coupons, Jetha gives him all of them except Babita's car coupon. On being asked, Jetha tries to ask Rustom Ji about the consequences if someone has misplaced or damaged the coupon. Rustom Ji informs Jetha that Ramsang Company doesn't qualify them as the winner, and they cancel the prize. What explanation will Jetha give to Babita this time?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3746, 15 Apr 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 32 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 32 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 13th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma

Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: Naagin 6 | नागिन 6 | Ep. 122 | Highlight | Raghu Apologizes To Prathna!
snippet.description:
Naagin 6 | नागिन 6 | Ep. 122 | Highlight| Raghu Apologizes To Prathna!

Suvarna gets shocked to see Meher and realizes she is Raghu and Prathna's long-lost daughter. Suvarna decides to tell the truth to Raghu and Prathna but is unable to do so. Will she be able to tell Raghu and Pratha the truth?

As Raghu saves Naina's life, Prathna thanks him and expresses her feelings for him. Raghu, however, refuses to forgive her for killing Meher. Elsewhere, Suvarna learns that Meher is Raghu and Prathna's daughter. Will Raghu discover Meher's identity?

snippet.title: Men's Locker Room Ep 06: KING | Paisa, Sacha Pyaar and Desi Hip-Hop | Part-1 | Tu maan meri jaan
snippet.description:
In this episode, we are in conversation with King, who is a rapper, singer, runner up of MTV Hustle season 1 and with his immensely popular track “Tu maan meri jaan”, has been a phenomenon on billboards.

He talks about why he took on the mononym, and how it’s befitting for him. He also talks about how fame and success have (and in some cases, haven’t) changed his life. He further continues and tells us how differentiating between who’s being real and who’s being fake after your success becomes really important.

He also delightedly shares how and where he spends money the most, and how he prefers to have his own choice and taste in things rather than going with exorbitantly priced things just to fit in. King also tells us how he absolutely loves food, especially his undying love for KFC.

He speaks on relationships being very important to him and how he believes in treasuring the people who were there with him from Day 1.

To know more about the surprisingly humble person, watch the full episode of Men's Locker Room with King

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3745 - 14 Apr 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3745: Is The Coupon At Risk?
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha assures Babita Ji that he will arrange the car for a day, but she must return it to him the next day for registration. Babita Ji is overjoyed at the news and praises Jetha for honoring her request. Jetha admires Bagha because it was his suggestion that led to Jetha obtaining the car from the Ramsang firm. Later, Bagha, Nattu Kaka, and Jetha begin to stamp the coupons, but the ink is accidentally spilled over them. Jetha becomes terrified when the coupon is spoiled. What happens next? Will Babita Ji now get the car? Keep watching to find out what happens next!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3745, 14 Apr 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS Man City 3-1 Leicester | Haaland (2), Stones, Iheanacho Goals
snippet.description:
City moved within three points of leaders Arsenal with a comfortable 3-1 win over Leicester.
The Blues swept the struggling Foxes aside in a blistering opening 24 minutes that saw John Stones score and Erling Haaland take his tally for the season to 47 with two more goals.
It looked as though there might be an avalanche of goals thereafter, but the visitors dug in and with both teams making numerous substitutions, the pattern of the game became somewhat disjointed.
Leicester's Kelechi Iheanacho pulled one back late on and also saw a shot strike the inside of the post, but it was too little, too late.

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 33 Teaser - 13th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 33 Teaser - 13th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: അമ്മയെ കൊലപ്പെടുത്തുന്നത് കണ്ട് പത്താം വയസ്സിൽ നാട് വിട്ട് കോടികൾ സമ്പാദിച്ച് തിരിച്ചെത്തിയപ്പോൾ
snippet.description:
നമ്മളിൽ നിന്നും വ്യത്യസ്ത ചിന്തകളുമായി ജിവിക്കുന്ന ആളുകൾ നമ്മുടെ ചുറ്റുപാടും ഉണ്ടാകും അങ്ങനെ വേറിട്ടു ജീവിക്കുന്ന ആളുകളെ നിങ്ങൾക്ക് അറിയാമെങ്കിൽ അറിയിക്കാൻ മറക്കല്ലേ നിങ്ങളുടെയൊക്കെ സപ്പോർട്ട് ഉണ്ടെങ്കിൽ നമുക്ക് ഇവരെയൊക്കെ പുറംലോകത്തേക്ക് കൊണ്ടുവരാം.🥰

snippet.title: தமிழ் வருடப் பிறப்பு 2023 | சித்திரை கனி காணுதல் | வழிபடும் நேரம் & முறை | Tamil New Year 2023
snippet.description:
சித்திரை மாதத்தில் பிறந்தவர்களும், குழந்தை பெற்றவர்களும் பார்க்க வேண்டிய பதிவு | Desa Mangayarkarasi
https://youtu.be/XxAB_XVBMZo

மருத்து நீராடி தமிழ்ப் புத்தாண்டை வரவேற்று வழிபடும் முறை | கனி காணுதல் | தமிழ் வருட பிறப்பு
https://youtu.be/0g00MJwEQNw

செல்வம், ஆரோக்கியம், நீண்ட ஆயுள் பெற தமிழ்ப் புத்தாண்டை வரவேற்று வழிபடும் முறை.   மேலும் கனி காணுதல், அறுசுவை உணவு படைத்தல், வழிபடும் நேரம் என பல தகவல்களை திருமதி. தேச மங்கையர்க்கரசி அம்மா அவர்கள் அளித்துள்ளார். 

- ஆத்ம ஞான மையம் 

# சித்திரை கனி காணுதல் 
# தமிழ் வருட பிறப்பு 
# Tamil New Year
# தமிழ்ப் புத்தாண்டு

snippet.title: AAP नेता Raghav Chadha ने Arvind Kejriwal की महात्मा गांधी से की तुलना
snippet.description:

Tere Bin Episode 31 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream - 12th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. *About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

*About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

snippet.title: 11 Flop Shows लगे Actress बनने में 👆 | Roopal Tyagi | Josh Talks Hindi
snippet.description:
Roopal Tyagi जी को मिला अपनी हर दिक्कत का Solution शिवा में
आपको भी मिलेगा English की हर दिक्कत का Solution Josh पर  👇
https://joshskills.app.link/7RAyXfvuXyb

Venue Partner for this talk: Recreate Studio
Location: Mumbai

TV actress Roopal Tyagi was only 16 years old when she came to Bombay with the dream of becoming an actor. She has taught dance to big actors like Shahid Kapoor, Kareena Kapoor, Neha Dhupia, and Vidya Balan. Roopal Tyagi has also appeared in reality shows like Bigg Boss and khatron ke khiladi. After 11 consecutive Flop shows, she got a chance to work in a big TV show Sapne suhane ladakpan ke which became a very popular TV Serial. Roopal Tyagi had to face many difficulties after her relationship broke up. Lies were also published about her in the newspapers but she never gave up.

Today Roopal Tyagi will tell us her life story through Josh Talks that how she became a successful actor. So do watch this Hindi Motivational/Inspirational video of Josh Talks completely.

TV Actress Roopal Tyagi सिर्फ़ 16 साल की थी जब बॉम्बे में अपने Actor बनने के सपने के साथ आईं. इन्होंने Shahid Kapoor, Kareena Kapoor, Neha Dhupiya और Vidya Balan जैसे बड़े-बड़े Actors को Dance सिखाया है. Roopal Tyagi Bigg Boss और Khatron Ke Khiladi जैसे Reality Shows में भी आई हैं. लगातार 11 Flop Shows के बाद इन्हें एक बड़ा TV Show 'Sapne Suhane Ladakpan Ke' में काम करने का मौका मिला जो काफ़ी ज़्यादा Poppulor TV Serial बन गया. Roopal Tyagi के Relationship के टूट जाने के बाद इन्हें कईं मुश्किलों का सामना करना पड़ा. अखबारों में इनके बारे झूट भी छापा गया पर इन्होंने कभी हार नहीं मानी. 

आज जोश Talks के माध्यम से Roopal Tyagi हमें सुनायेंगी अपनी Life Story कि कैसे ये एक Successful Actor बनी. तो जोश Talks की इस Hindi Motivational/inspirational video को पूरा ज़रूर देखें.  

#JoshTalksHindi #RoopalTyagiJoshTalks #RoopalTyagi #sapnesuhaneladakpanke #tvstar 

ऐसे ही Famous Actors और Bollywood Celebrities की Talks अभी देखें - 

Vishal Malhotra Josh Talks - https://youtu.be/ziYCMlg5VZo 
Anup Soni Josh Talks - https://youtu.be/wWDRAAArpkg
Actor Shyam Pathak Josh Talks - https://youtu.be/s8gIInusOmQ
Aasif Khan Josh Talks - https://youtu.be/ZHPYPpQvmXU
Sanjay Mishra Josh Talks - https://youtu.be/qJUDTxk8an8
Veebha Anand Josh Talks - https://youtu.be/fbgVjTYnyEg

Josh Talks Hindi aims to inspire and motivate you by bringing to you the best Hindi motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 7 regional languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the challenges they face in their careers or business and helping them discover their true calling in life. 

“ज़िंदगी में कुछ बड़ा करने के लिए जोश का होना बहुत ज़रूरी है.” 
इसी सोच के साथ एक शुरुआत हुई. देश के कोने-कोने से सबसे प्रेरणादायक कहानियों को चुनकर हर उस शख्स तक पहुंचाने की जो बड़े सपने देखता है. 
इसी सोच का नाम है जोश Talks. 
वो मंच जहां कई Role Models आते हैं और अपने जीवन की प्रेरणादायक कहानी हमारे साथ शेयर करते हैं. वो अपने जीवन के उन किस्सों को शेयर करते हैं जहां वो Fail हुए, उन्होंने गलतियां की, कई बार हिम्मत भी टूटी पर अपने लक्ष्य को हासिल करके ही माने. 

अगर दो शब्दों में कहा जाए, तो जोश Talks हम सबके लिए हमारे ‘बड़े भैय्या/बड़ी बहन’ की तरह है. 
जो हमेशा हमारे दोस्त बनकर हमारी बात सुनते हैं और हमें कुछ नया सिखाते हैं.
तो चलो, जोश के साथ हर Goal को हासिल करें. :)

और हां! अगर हमारे पास ऐसे लोगों की कहानियां हैं जिन्होंने अपनी मेहनत और हिम्मत के दम पर अच्छा मुकाम हासिल किया है. जिससे आज वो समाज के लिए एक Role Model बन गए हैं. 
तो, अभी लिखकर भेज देते हैं - speakers@joshtalks.com

► जोश Talks Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/JoshTalksHindi​ 
► जोश Talks Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/JoshTalksHi...

All of the views and work outside the pretext of the video of the speaker, are his/ her own, and Josh Talks, by any means, does not support them directly or indirectly and neither is it liable for it. Viewers are requested to use their own discretion while viewing the content and focus on the entirety of the story rather than finding inferences in its parts.
